00:01:59.300 --> 00:02:05.200
of people from starving. Today, in the United States,
less than 1% of people list their occupation as farming.

00:02:05.209 --> 00:02:08.580
I mean, we’ve come so far that we don’t
even have to farm flowers anymore. Stan, are

